<% text_for :title do %>
  You’ll need a visa to come to the UK
<% end %>

<% govspeak_for :body do %>
  <%= render partial: 'stateless_or_refugee', locals: {calculator: calculator} %>

  <%= render partial: 'estonia_or_latvia', locals: {calculator: calculator} %>

  Apply for a [Marriage Visitor visa](/marriage-visa) if you and your partner want to get married or enter into a civil partnership in the UK.

  <% if calculator.passport_country_is_saudi_arabia_or_bahrain? %>
    If you want to live in the UK permanently, you must apply for a [family visa](/uk-family-visa) if your partner is any of the following:

    + a British citizen
    + settled in the UK
    + someone with humanitarian protection, for example if they have refugee status

    ^If you want to convert a civil partnership into a marriage, you’ll need to apply for an [electronic visa waiver (EVW)](/get-electronic-visa-waiver) or a [Standard Visitor visa](/standard-visitor).^
  <% else %>
    If you want to live in the UK permanently, you must apply for a [family visa](/join-family-in-uk) if your partner:

    + is a British citizen
    + is settled in the UK (called having ‘indefinite leave to remain’)
    + has settled or pre-settled status under the EU Settlement Scheme
    + has a Turkish worker or businessperson visa
  <% end %>

  <% if calculator.passport_country_is_el_salvador? %>
    ##If you want to convert a civil partnership into a marriage

    You can come to the UK for up to 6 months without a visa if all of the following apply:

    * you booked your journey to the UK before 4pm UK time 11 May 2022 (9am El Salvador time) - for example, if you bought your plane ticket before 4pm 11 May 2022
    * you're arriving in the UK before 9 June 2022
    * you meet the [Standard Visitor eligibility requirements](/standard-visitor)

    [Check what documents you need to bring](/government/publications/visitor-visa-guide-to-supporting-documents) to show officers at the UK border.

    ###If you need to leave and re-enter the UK

    You'll need a visa to re-enter the UK if either of the following apply:

    * you did not book your return journey to the UK before 4pm UK time 11 May 2022 (9am El Salvador time)
    * you're returning to the UK after 8 June 2022
  <% end %>
<% end %>
